<item>
            <title>[SOLR-6223] SearchComponents may throw NPE when using shards.tolerant and there is a failure in the &#8220;GET_FIELDS/GET_HIGHLIGHTS/GET_DEBUG&#8221; phase</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-6223</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I found that, when using shards.tolerant, if there is some kind of exception in the second phase of the search, some component&#8217;s throw NPE. &lt;br/&gt;
I found it with the QueryComponent first, but then saw that other components would suffer in the same way: DebugComponent, HighlightComponent and MLTComponent. I only checked the components of the default chain.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
